{
  "id": "SO-021",
  "title": "LOTO with M-CNC-01",
  "risk": "The planner can extract the machine id but still ask for it again, route to generic machine status, or omit RAG/source evidence for the LOTO procedure.",
  "prompt": "What is the LOTO procedure for M-CNC-01?",
